The '''Shak clan''' was a [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] family on [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]].

In the early years of the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]], the Shak clan operated the [[Kala'uun Starport]], from which they operated a number of illegal activities, including [[Ryll/Legends|ryll]] scams and [[Slavery/Legends|slave]] sales. Due to their ryll scams against the [[New Republic/Legends|New Republic]] in [[6 ABY/Legends|6 ABY]], the clan was discredited and stripped of its prominence.

